      <title>《信贷周刊》：德国银行开始削减引发债券市场动荡的美国办公楼贷款敞口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/german-banks-start-to-cut-us-office-loan-exposure-that-caused-bond-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对商业房地产损失的担忧导致 2 月份债券和股票价格暴跌，德国银行正在削减美国办公室的遗留贷款敞口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/german-banks-start-to-cut-us-office-loan-exposure-that-caused-bond-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 02 Nov 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
